ge of 18 or 19. Her story has captured the imagination of many writers, and she is variously portrayed as a national and political hero, a model of apolitical straightforwardness and honesty, and a religious heroine. She was canonized in  1920 . More recent influences have included the American film actress  Joan Crawford  (  1908–77 , born  Lucille le Sueur ), the British actress  Joan Collins  (  b. 1933 ), the American comedienne  Joan Rivers  (  b. 1933 ), and the West Indian pop singer  Joan Armatrading  (  b. 1950 )."],"variants":[{"name":"John","meanings":["New Testament: ‘God is gracious’.  See  <b>John</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Joan had at least 1 son with John Shottisbroke."},"et":{"–Deceased":"Surnud","1275–1306":"1275–1306","1295–Male":"1295–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","1306":"1306"},"fi":{"–Deceased":"Kuollut","1275–1306":"1275–1306","1295–Male":"1295–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","1306":"1306"},"fr":{"–Deceased":"Décédée","1275–1306":"1275–1306","1295–Male":"1295–Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","1306":"1306","lifeSummary":"Joan a eu au moins 1 fils avec John Shottisbroke."},"de":{"–Deceased":"Verstorben","1275–1306":"1275–1306","1295–Male":"1295–Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","1306":"1306","lifeSummary":"Joan hatte mit John Shottisbroke mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"–Deceased":"Desede","1275–1306":"1275–1306","1295–Male":"1295–Desede","–Female":"Desede","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","1306":"1306"},"hu":{"–Deceased":"elhunyt","1275–1306":"1275–1306","1295–Male":"1295–elhunyt","–Female":"elhunyt","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","1306":"1306"},"id":{"–Deceased":"Telah Meninggal","1275–1306":"1275–1306","1295–Male":"1295–Telah Meninggal","–Female":"Telah Meninggal","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","1306":"1306"},"it":{"–Deceased":"Deceduta","1275–1306":"1275–1306","1295–Male":"1295–Deceduto","–Female":"Deceduta","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","1306":"1306","lifeS